#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:1
msgid "Billing a month, step by step"
msgstr ""
"Een maand factureren in het WZC met Resthome, stap voor stap: van de periode"
" tot de eFact-verzending van de RIZIV-forfaits naar de mutualiteit."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:4
msgid ""
"Billing a month in a nursing home (MR/MRS) with Resthome, step by step: from"
" the period to the eFact submission of the INAMI packages to the insurer."
msgstr ""
"Een maand factureren in een woonzorgcentrum (WZC) met Resthome, stap voor "
"stap: van de periode tot de eFact-verzending van de RIZIV-forfaits naar de "
"mutualiteit."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:8
msgid "How do I bill a month in Resthome?"
msgstr "Hoe factureer ik een maand in Resthome?"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:9
msgid ""
"Open the month's period, generate, review (MDA, Katz, anomalies), create the"
" invoices (resident's share and insurer's share), post them, then generate "
"and send the eFact to the insurers."
msgstr ""
"Open de periode van de maand, genereer, controleer (MDA, Katz, afwijkingen),"
" maak de facturen aan (bewoners- en mutualiteitsaandeel), boek ze, en "
"genereer en verstuur dan de eFact naar de verzekeringsinstellingen."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:11
msgid "In what order should I bill?"
msgstr "In welke volgorde moet ik factureren?"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:12
msgid ""
"Always: Generate → review → Create invoices → post → Generate eFact → send →"
" track the responses. Check insurability (MDA) before billing."
msgstr ""
"Altijd: Genereren → controleren → Facturen aanmaken → boeken → eFact "
"genereren → versturen → antwoorden opvolgen. Controleer de verzekerbaarheid "
"(MDA) vóór u factureert."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:14
msgid "Can I make corrections after billing?"
msgstr "Kan ik corrigeren na het factureren?"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:15
msgid ""
"As long as the eFact has not been sent, you can set the period back to "
"draft. After sending, correct via a credit note or a corrective batch."
msgstr ""
"Zolang de eFact niet verstuurd is, kunt u de periode terug naar concept "
"zetten. Na verzending corrigeert u via een creditnota of een corrigerend "
"lot."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:18
msgid ""
"This guide walks you **from start to finish** through a billing month: open "
"the period, check insurability, generate the invoices, post them, then "
"**send the insurer's share via eFact** and track the responses. Follow it "
"with Resthome open alongside: each step tells you **where to click**."
msgstr ""
"Deze gids begeleidt u **van begin tot eind** van een facturatiemaand: de "
"periode openen, de verzekerbaarheid controleren, de facturen genereren, ze "
"boeken, en daarna **het mutualiteitsaandeel via eFact versturen** en de "
"antwoorden opvolgen. Volg ze met Resthome ernaast open: elke stap geeft aan "
"**waar te klikken**."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:23
msgid "The idea in two parts"
msgstr "Het idee in twee delen"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:26
msgid "Each month is billed in **two flows**:"
msgstr "Elke maand wordt gefactureerd in **twee stromen**:"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:28
msgid ""
"the **resident's share** — accommodation, supplements and supplement "
"agreements, care services, medication, adjusted for absences → standard "
"invoices;"
msgstr ""
"het **bewonersaandeel** — huisvesting, supplementen en "
"supplementenovereenkomsten, zorgprestaties, geneesmiddelen, aangepast aan de"
" afwezigheden → klassieke facturen;"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:30
msgid ""
"the **insurer's share** (INAMI package) → **eFact** submission to the "
"insurers."
msgstr ""
"het **mutualiteitsaandeel** (RIZIV-forfait) → **eFact**-verzending naar de "
"verzekeringsinstellingen."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:32
msgid "Resthome runs them in parallel on a single **period**."
msgstr "Resthome voert ze parallel uit op eenzelfde **periode**."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:35
msgid "Step 1 — Open the month's period"
msgstr "Stap 1 — De maandperiode openen"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:37
msgid "Main menu → **MR/MRS** app."
msgstr "Hoofdmenu → toepassing **MR/MRS**."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:38
msgid "**Billing → Billing periods**."
msgstr "**Facturatie → Facturatieperiodes**."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:39
msgid "Open the month's period, or create it with **New period**."
msgstr "Open de periode van de maand, of maak ze aan met **Nieuwe periode**."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:41
msgid ""
"The period lists the residents concerned and its **status** at the top "
"(Draft → Generated → Invoiced → Closed)."
msgstr ""
"De periode toont de betrokken bewoners en haar **status** bovenaan (concept "
"→ gegenereerd → gefactureerd → afgesloten)."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:44
msgid "Step 2 — Check insurability (MDA)"
msgstr "Stap 2 — De verzekerbaarheid controleren (MDA)"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:46
msgid "Before billing the insurer, check that everyone is **in order**:"
msgstr ""
"Vóór u de mutualiteit factureert, controleer dat iedereen **in orde** is:"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:48
msgid "On the period, click **Check MDA** (batch check)."
msgstr "Klik op de periode op **MDA controleren** (bulkcontrole)."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:49
msgid ""
"Wait for the responses; fix the flagged cases (wrong insurer, loss of "
"insurability)."
msgstr ""
"Wacht op de antwoorden; corrigeer de gesignaleerde gevallen (verkeerde "
"mutualiteit, verlies van verzekerbaarheid)."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:52
msgid ""
"This is the step that avoids rejections later. Details: [Insurability "
"(MDA)](../ehealth/mda.md)."
msgstr ""
"Dit is de stap die latere weigeringen vermijdt. Details: [Verzekerbaarheid "
"(MDA)](../ehealth/mda.md)."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:55
msgid "Step 3 — Generate the billing lines"
msgstr "Stap 3 — De factuurregels genereren"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:57
msgid "Click **Generate**."
msgstr "Klik **Genereren**."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:58
msgid ""
"For each resident, Resthome computes: **accommodation**, **package** (on the"
" days present), **supplements** and **supplement agreements**, **care "
"services**, **medication**, and applies the **absences**."
msgstr ""
"Resthome berekent voor elke bewoner: **verblijf**, **forfait** (op de "
"aanwezigheidsdagen), **supplementen** en **supplementenovereenkomsten**, "
"**zorgprestaties**, **geneesmiddelen**, en past de **afwezigheden** toe."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:62
msgid "Advance billing"
msgstr "Anticipatief"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:65
msgid ""
"Accommodation is billed **one month in advance**; the package and "
"supplements for the month served. See [Overview](index.md)."
msgstr ""
"Het verblijf wordt **een maand op voorhand** gefactureerd; het forfait en de"
" supplementen op de gepresteerde maand. Zie [Overzicht](index.md)."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:69
msgid "Step 4 — Create the invoices (resident's share)"
msgstr "Stap 4 — De facturen aanmaken (bewonersaandeel)"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:71
msgid "Click **Create invoices**."
msgstr "Klik **Facturen aanmaken**."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:72
msgid "The **draft** invoices for the resident's share are generated."
msgstr "De **concept**facturen van het bewonersaandeel worden gegenereerd."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:73
msgid "Check them, then **Post** them."
msgstr "Kijk ze na, en **boek** ze."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:75
msgid "A posted invoice \"freezes\" the month"
msgstr "Een geboekte factuur « bevriest » de maand"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:78
msgid ""
"Once **posted**, a resident's invoice is locked for that month (protection)."
" To correct it: set it back to **draft** or issue a **credit note**, then "
"**Refresh**. Other residents are not affected."
msgstr ""
"Eenmaal **geboekt** is de factuur van een bewoner vergrendeld voor die maand"
" (bescherming). Om ze te corrigeren: zet ze terug naar **concept** of maak "
"een **creditnota**, en **vernieuw** dan. De andere bewoners worden niet "
"geraakt."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:83
msgid "Step 5 — Generate the eFact (insurer's share)"
msgstr "Stap 5 — De eFact genereren (mutualiteitsaandeel)"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:85
msgid "Once the invoices are posted:"
msgstr "Zodra de facturen geboekt zijn:"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:87
msgid "On the period, click **Generate eFact**."
msgstr "Klik op de periode op **eFact genereren**."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:88
msgid ""
"Resthome builds the eFact **batches**, **grouped by union** of insurers."
msgstr ""
"Resthome stelt de eFact-**loten** samen, **gegroepeerd per unie** van "
"verzekeringsinstellingen."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:90
msgid "Step 6 — Send to the insurers"
msgstr "Stap 6 — Versturen naar de verzekeringsinstellingen"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:92
msgid "Open **eHealth → eFact → Cockpit** (or the batches)."
msgstr "Open **eHealth → eFact → Cockpit** (of de loten)."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:93
msgid "Click **Send all** (or send batch by batch)."
msgstr "Klik **Alles versturen** (of verstuur lot per lot)."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:94
msgid "The submissions go out to the insurers via the eHealth network."
msgstr ""
"De verzendingen vertrekken naar de mutualiteiten via het eHealth-netwerk."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:96
msgid "Step 7 — Track the responses"
msgstr "Stap 7 — De antwoorden opvolgen"

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:98
msgid ""
"Click **Fetch responses** to bring back the acknowledgements and "
"settlements."
msgstr ""
"Klik **Antwoorden ophalen** om de ontvangstbewijzen en afrekeningen binnen "
"te halen."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:99
msgid ""
"Each batch moves through **Sent → Acknowledged → Accepted / Rejected**."
msgstr ""
"Elk lot gaat **Verstuurd → Ontvangstbewijs ontvangen → Aanvaard / "
"Geweigerd**."

#: ../../content/facturation/facturer-un-mois.md:100
msgid ""
"In case of a **rejection**, fix the cause (insurability, dates, amounts) and"
" **resend**."
msgstr ""
"Bij een **weigering**, corrigeer de oorzaak (verzekerbaarheid, data, "
"bedragen) en **verstuur opnieuw**."

